data.description: No HOA, Allen ISD,Welcome to this stunning & spacious property nestled on an oversized lot, this house boasts 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2.5  bathrooms. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the large formal living & dining areas. These rooms seamlessly flow into the heart of the home, which has an open kitchen & kitchen nook, which seamlessly connects to the living room, where a grand fireplace takes center stage, creating a cozy and inviting ambiance. Natural light floods this space. Step through the living room to access the expansive backyard. This remarkable corner lot provides ample space for all your outdoor activities. Upstairs, all 4 bedrooms offer spacious retreats, each featuring ample closet space. The guest bathrooms has been remodeled. Thee master bedroom. It features its own ensuite, complete with a generously sized closet, a soothing garden tub, & an elegant shower. This is your private sanctuary, a space to unwind and rejuvenate after a long day.
